properties.abstract: It is obvious why Silberplatten has its name: the slab made of compact limestone glitters silvery in the sun. Of course, there is no silver to be found, but instead an itinerary winding its way up to the summit. Climbing is not required.
properties.subtitle: Better silver than gold?
properties.title: From Schwägalp, descent to Unterwasser

sac_photos.title: The itinerary on Silberplatte just before the summit
View to the first part of the tour: on the right the grassy Grenzchopf, then Silberplatten, Silberplattenköpfe, Stosssattel (which you cross) and Stoss

segments.description: From Schwägalp follow the «Grüeziweg» to Tierwies. From there follow a trail up and down almost to the saddle at P. 2072 (sometimes called Silberplattensattel).
segments.title: Schwägalp – saddle at P. 2027

segments.description:
As soon as the white-red-white marked hiking trail descends southward, leave it to traverse on the ridge and past an exposed passage (T4) to reach the saddle. From the saddle ascend among boulders until below the slab. Slightly ascending, traverse eastward (right) until you reach a characteristic gully at the end of the slab. Scramble up the gully, and in an arc from left to right ascend to the roomy summit, overcoming a short climbing passage. With good visibility the itinerary is easy to find. 
The descent back to the saddle at P. 2072 is on the ascent.

photos.caption: Climbers descending the slab a few metres below the summit

segments.title: Saddle at P. 2072 - Silberplatten and back

segments.description: There are many variants for the descent. The most interesting is as follows: from the saddle descend to the hiking trail, negotiating a short escarpment. The trail goes around the climbing faces of Silberplatten to reach Stosssattel (2042 m). Continue on this hiking trail across the saddle at Lauchwies and past the Schrenit and the Trosen alp to the picturesque Alpli. On a sunny day with a lot of visitors you have a good chance to hitch a ride to Unterwasser. If you hike down (1 Std.), do not forget to make a little detour to visit the Thurfälle waterfall.
segments.title: Saddle at P. 2072 - Stosssattel - Alpli - Unterwasser
